    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready to hit the road in style with this fantastic find! This vehicle is in truly good condition, having been well-maintained and cared for over the years. It offers a smooth, reliable ride and a clean interior that shows just how much it was appreciated by its previous owner. While you might find a few minor signs of normal use, it's a solid, dependable choice that's ready for many more miles of adventure!",
