      "description": "Presenting a vehicle of uncompromising standards. This specimen remains in showroom condition, exhibiting a level of care that borders on the obsessive. Every detail, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior appointments, reflects a heritage of meticulous maintenance. This is an investment-grade acquisition for the discerning enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 46500.0,
